==English==
===Etymology===
Arabic {{ARchar|ذنب الكيتوس}} (''dhanab al-kaytūs'') ‘Cetus's tail’, from {{ARchar|[[ذنب]]}} ‘tail’ + an Arabisation of [[Cetus]].

===Noun===
'''Deneb Kaitos'''
# the brightest [[star]] in the [[constellation]] [[Cetus]]

